data.meta_description: Download Images of Adelaide Of Austria - Free for commercial use, no attribution required. From: Maria Adelaide of Austria queen of Sardinia to {{to}.
data.text:
She is 26 years old and already mother of five children. She stands on the terrace of her palais with a wonderful evening landscape in background. Seven years after the portrait's creation she would die.
